OL,3,CThames Water says it must hike
OL,4,Ccustomer bills by nearly 60% by 2030
OL,6,FThames Water has said it needs to hike
OL,7,Fcustomer bills by up to nearly 60% by
OL,8,F2030 or warned it will become
OL,9,F"uninvestable".
OL,11,FBritain's biggest water supplier made
OL,12,Fthe shock demand in its response to
OL,13,FOfwat's proposals to cap household
OL,14,Fwater charges.
OL,16,FOfwat proposed in its draft
OL,17,Fdetermination in July that water firms
OL,18,Fshould be allowed to increase bills by
OL,19,Fa third less than they had requested
OL,20,Fon average, capping it at around #19
OL,21,Fextra a year.
