OL,3,CThames Water says it must hike
OL,4,Ccustomer bills by nearly 60% by 2030
OL,6,FThames Water put forward plans in
OL,7,FApril to increase bills by 44% in the
OL,8,Ffive years to 2030.
OL,10,FBut Ofwat has proposed that Thames
OL,11,FWater bill increases should be capped
OL,12,Fat 23% over that period and spending
OL,13,Fat #16.9 billion.
OL,15,FDebt-laden Thames Water has now come
OL,16,Fback saying that it believes customer
OL,17,Fbills need to rise by far more than
OL,18,FOfwat has proposed ` and even more
OL,19,Fthan the firm itself first put forward.
