OL,3,CThames Water says it must hike
OL,4,Ccustomer bills by nearly 60% by 2030
OL,6,FThe water company proposed raising
OL,7,Faverage yearly water bills to as much
OL,8,Fas #696, a 59% increase, if it is
OL,9,Fgiven extra spending allowances by the
OL,10,Fregulator.
OL,12,FThe average bill over the five-year
OL,13,Fperiod from 2025 to 2030 would be #638
OL,14,Funder the proposal. Average bills in
OL,15,F2023 to 2024 were #433.
