OL,3,CThames Water says it must hike
OL,4,Ccustomer bills by nearly 60% by 2030
OL,6,FChris Weston, chief executive of
OL,7,FThames Water, said: "The money we're
OL,8,Fasking for from customers will be
OL,9,Finvested in new infrastructure and
OL,10,Fimproving our services for the benefit
OL,11,Fof households and the environment.
OL,13,F"They are not being asked to pay
OL,14,Ftwice, but to make up for years of
OL,15,Ffocus on keeping bills low."
