OL,3,CThames Water says it must hike
OL,4,Ccustomer bills by nearly 60% by 2030
OL,6,FIt comes as the water sector issued a
OL,7,Fwarning to Ofwat that its bill cap
OL,8,Fplans could create a "material risk"
OL,9,Fthat suppliers may fail to raise
OL,10,Fenough cash to invest in stopping
OL,11,Fsewage leaks.
OL,13,FThames Water said the main driver of
OL,14,Fthe latest increase is "due to an
OL,15,Fupdate to our customer numbers which
OL,16,Fsees a customer reduction from our
OL,17,Foriginal plan", as well as previously
OL,18,Fforecast increases in spending.
