OL,3,CThames Water says it must hike
OL,4,Ccustomer bills by nearly 60% by 2030
OL,6,FThe company said it wants to invest
OL,7,F#20.7 billion in its services over the
OL,8,Fperiod, including upgrading its ageing
OL,9,Finfrastructure.
OL,11,FThames Water is also in the grip of a
OL,12,Ffunding crisis and has more than #15
OL,13,Fbillion of debt, casting uncertainty
OL,14,Fover its future.
OL,16,FIt said in July that it only has
OL,17,Fenough money to continue trading until
OL,18,Fthe end of May 2025.
